4 SJR___ RECOGNIZING AND CONGRATULATING THE ALABAMA SCHOOL OF
5 MATHEMATICS AND SCIENCE ON THEIR 2026 NATIONAL RANKING AS
6 THE #19 BEST PUBLIC HIGH SCHOOL IN AMERICA AND #1 IN
7 ALABAMA.
8
9 WHEREAS, the Alabama School of Mathematics and
10 Science (ASMS), located in Mobile, Alabama, has earned
11 national recognition for academic excellence by being ranked
12 #19 Best Public High School in America for 2026 by Niche,
13 one of the nation's leading college and school search
14 platforms, out of more than 20,000 public high schools
15 nationwide; and
16 WHEREAS, ASMS was also named the #1 Best Public High
17 School in Alabama, marking the second consecutive year it
18 has received this distinction, and further earned top
19 statewide rankings as the #1 Best High School for STEM, #1
20 Best College Prep Public High School, and #1 Best Magnet
21 High School in Alabama; and
22 WHEREAS, ASMS is uniquely distinguished as Alabama's
23 only 100 percent residential public high school, serving
24 students in grades 10-12 from all 67 counties across the
25 state, who live and learn on campus in Mobile at no cost for
26 tuition; and
27 WHEREAS, the school provides a rigorous academic
28 environment in which expert faculty deliver advanced and
Page 1

environment in which expert faculty deliver advanced and
SJR32 Enrolled
29 college-level coursework, complemented by meaningful
30 research opportunities that prepare students for success in
31 higher education and competitive careers in science,
32 technology, engineering, mathematics, and related fields;
33 and
34 WHEREAS, the 2026 rankings reflect ASMS's exceptional
35 performance across multiple indicators evaluated by Niche,
36 including academic outcomes, extracurricular opportunities,
37 data from sources such as the United States Department of
38 Education, and feedback from students, parents, and alumni;
39 and
40 WHEREAS, through its statewide mission, residential
41 model, and commitment to academic excellence, the Alabama
42 School of Mathematics and Science continues to elevate
43 educational opportunities for Alabama's most talented
44 students, while bringing national distinction to the City of
45 Mobile and the State of Alabama; now therefore,
46 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA, BOTH
47 HOUSES THEREOF CONCURRING, That we hereby recognize and
48 congratulate the Alabama School of Mathematics and Science
49 on its outstanding 2026 national ranking as the #19 Best
50 Public High School in America and its continued designation
51 as the #1 Public High School in Alabama.
